"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:9.4.3\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">9.4.3</span> 標題：個（餅）（loaf）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： כִּכָּר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kikar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:23\">EXO 29:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:5\">JDG 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:36\">1SA 2:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:3\">1SA 10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:3\">1CH 16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:26\">PRO 6:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:21\">JER 37:21</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： צְלִיל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tslil)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:13\">JDG 7:13</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0527_bread_tandir.jpg\" alt=\"一疊扁麵包（圓麵餅）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">一疊扁麵包（圓麵餅） (© jeffreyw, CC BY 2.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>「個」是餅的量詞。餅一般是扁圓形的，大約有手指張開後的一隻手那麼大。不過，餅的大小和形狀可能有很大的差別。經文提到有三種餅：第一種小餅和今天的麵包卷或餅乾類似；第二種餅大又圓；第三種餅扁而薄，用來像勺子一樣舀食物吃。一般來說，比較富有的人吃小麥做的餅，窮人吃大麥做的餅（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:13\">JDG 7:13</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:7\">JHN 6:7</a> ）。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0527_bread_tandir.jpg\" alt=\"一疊扁麵包（圓麵餅）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">一疊扁麵包（圓麵餅） (© jeffreyw, CC BY 2.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>大多數有「餅」一詞的語言也會有表示「餅」的量詞。在很多經文中，「餅」就表示「一個餅」的意思（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">9.4 餅、麵包 (bread)&lt;REALIA:9.4&gt;</a> 中的討論）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:13\">JDG 7:13</a> ：在這節經文中，這個大麥餅的重要特徵是它滾下了山。如果目標語言根據形狀來區分餅的種類，那麼這裡適合採用表示圓餅的詞。</p>\n<p>聖餅、陳設餅、供餅：參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.3.5.1 供餅 (consecrated bread, bread of the presence, showbread)&lt;REALIA:4.3.5.1&gt;</a> 。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
